:R-HSA-4641258  a           owl:NamedIndividual , obo:GO_0090090 ;
        rdfs:comment        "DVL protein levels are regulated by both proteasomal and lysosomal degradation (reviewed in Gao and Chen, 2010). The E3 ligases HECF1, ITCH and KLHL12:CUL3 have all been shown to contribute to the polyubiquitination and subsequent degradation of DVL (Angers et al, 2006; Miyazaki et al, 2004; Wei et al, 2012). DVL stability is also regulated by its interaction with DACT1, which promotes degradation of DVL in the lysosome (Cheyette et al, 2002; Zhang et al, 2006)." ;
        rdfs:label          "Degradation of DVL" ;
        dc:contributor      "Reviewed: van Amerongen, R, 2014-02-14" , "Reviewed: Rajakulendran, Nishani, 2014-01-22" , "Reviewed: Kikuchi, Akira, 2014-04-22" , "GOC:reactome_curators" , "Authored: Rothfels, K, 2013-06-24" , "Edited: Gillespie, ME, 2013-10-02" , "Edited: Matthews, L, 2007-09-04 11:49:29" ;
        dc:date             "2026-06-29" ;
        pav:providedBy      "https://reactome.org" ;
        oboInOwl:hasDbXref  "R-HSA-4641258" ;
        skos:narrower       <http://model.geneontology.org/R-HSA-201681/R-HSA-201681> ;
        skos:note           "org.biopax.paxtools.model.level3.Pathway" .

